public abstract class ParticipantController<C extends ParticipantInputCommand>
extends AutomaticSaveAjaxableFormController<C,Participant,ParticipantDao>

Base Controller class to handle the basic work flow in the Creation / Updation of a NewParticipantCommand Design This uses AbstractTabbedFlowFormController to implement tabbed workflow
